text: Sinocyclocheilus jinxiensis is a species of cavefish in the family Cyprinidae endemic to Xiaolong Spring in Jinxi County, Guangxi, China. In 2016, it was proposed that this species should be moved to its own genus Pseudosinocyclocheilus. ==References== Category:Cave fish Category:Sinocyclocheilus Category:Fish described in 2012
title: Sinocyclocheilus jinxiensis
